OL,3,CWynne Evans to step back from Strictly
OL,4,Ctour after 'unacceptable' comment
OL,6,FWelsh opera singer Wynne Evans has
OL,7,Fsaid he's to "take some time out" from
OL,8,Fhis radio show and the Strictly Come
OL,9,FDancing live tour.
OL,11,FIt's after he apologised for an
OL,12,F"inappropriate and unacceptable"
OL,13,Fremark made during the tour launch
OL,14,Fearlier in the month.
OL,16,FHe said: "I've agreed with the BBC
OL,17,Fthat I'll take some time out from my
OL,18,Fradio show and the Strictly Live tour,
OL,19,Fas well as my other public
OL,20,Fcommitments, to prioritise my
OL,21,Fwellbeing.
