OL,3,CWynne Evans to step back from Strictly
OL,4,Ctour after 'unacceptable' comment
OL,6,F"I am deeply sorry for the pain my
OL,7,Finappropriate actions have caused, and
OL,8,Fplan to take this time for self-
OL,9,Freflection.
OL,11,F"Apologies to those I won't get to see
OL,12,Fat the remaining performances and I'm
OL,13,Fgrateful to my fellow tour gang for
OL,14,Fall the amazing support they have
OL,15,Fgiven me."
OL,17,FThe Welsh radio presenter and opera
OL,18,Fsinger is facing backlash after making
OL,19,Fa sexualised comment during the launch
OL,20,Fevent for the Strictly Come Dancing
OL,21,Flive tour on January 16.
