OL,3,CWynne Evans to step back from Strictly
OL,4,Ctour after 'unacceptable' comment
OL,6,FEvans, who appeared on the BBC One
OL,7,Fshow last year alongside dance partner
OL,8,FKatya Jones, was reportedly filmed
OL,9,Fmaking the remark to a woman during
OL,10,Fthe event.
OL,12,FThe Mail on Sunday first reported the
OL,13,Fincident, which quickly gained
OL,14,Fattention after a video surfaced.
OL,16,FThe PA News Agency says Evans was
OL,17,Fgiven a formal warning by tour
OL,18,Fproducers in response to the comment.
