OL,3,CWynne Evans to step back from Strictly
OL,4,Ctour after 'unacceptable' comment
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Strictly live
OL,7,Ftour and BBC Studios said that they
OL,8,Fhad not been made aware of any
OL,9,Fcomplaints prior to the video
OL,10,Femerging, but emphasised that such
OL,11,Fbehaviour would not be tolerated on
OL,12,Fthe tour.
OL,14,F"We have made it very clear to Wynne
OL,15,Fthat we do not condone such remarks,"
OL,16,Fthe spokesperson said.
OL,18,FThe incident has led to Evans stepping
OL,19,Fback from his usual role on BBC Radio
OL,20,FWales, with presenter Robin Morgan
OL,21,Ffilling in for him.
